<h1><span>Team Name: We Deny The Existence of Other Games In Town (Sigma-3, &quot;Bibliographers&quot;)</span></h1>
<p><strong>Team Members: <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gaffsey" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6590029); return false;">Gaffsey</a></span> (<em>Captain</em>), <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thedeadlymoose" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(732274); return false;">thedeadlymoose</a></span>, <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/twistedgears" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1735681); return false;">TwistedGears</a></span>, <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dexanote" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(481882); return false;">Dexanote</a></span></strong></p>
