<li><strong><a href="/nope-not-typing-all-that">Site 11, Conference Room K, 8:58 AM, July 12, 1982</a></strong> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gaffsey" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6590029); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6590029&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1594699572" alt="Gaffsey" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6590029)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gaffsey" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6590029); return false;">Gaffsey</a></span></li>
